_sText:
Well, what can I say most times I go on a new JailBreak I hear someone complaining that the map is to boring. So, for this map I made it as fun as possible! There are loads of games to play like: Volley ball, a maze, Rockclimb and many more! Plus there are also many places that players not playing can spectate from! ENJOY! Also special thankz to .doM for help during the mapping period.

Cheerz, Raffa.

p.s There was a glich for one of the cell buttons. I fixed it and it should work well now!
